---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="mt-20 border-t border-zinc-100 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-xl relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Decorative background elements -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-zinc-200 to-transparent"></div>
    
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 lg:gap-8">
            <!-- Brand Column -->
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <a href="/" class="flex flex-col">
                    <span class="font-black text-2xl tracking-tighter leading-none">INOX LINK</span>
                    <span class="text-[10px] text-zinc-500 font-bold tracking-[0.2em] mt-2 uppercase">Aço em Conexão</span>
                </a>
                <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed max-w-xs">
                    Sua principal fonte de informação, notícias e conhecimento técnico sobre o universo do aço inoxidável. Do mercado às especificações técnicas.
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <a href="#" class="p-2 rounded-full border border-zinc-100 text-zinc-400 hover:text-black hover:border-black transition-all" aria-label="LinkedIn">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M16 8a6 6 0 0 1 6 6v7h-4v-7a2 2 0 0 0-2-2 2 2 0 0 0-2 2v7h-4v-7a6 6 0 0 1 6-6z"/><rect width="4" height="12" x="2" y="9"/><circle cx="4" cy="4" r="2"/></svg>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#" class="p-2 rounded-full border border-zinc-100 text-zinc-400 hover:text-black hover:border-black transition-all" aria-label="Instagram">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="20" height="20" x="2" y="2" rx="5" ry="5"/><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"/><line x1="17.5" x2="17.51" y1="6.5" y2="6.5"/></svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Quick Links -->
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-zinc-900 mb-6">Navegação</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-4">
                    <li><a href="/" class="text-sm text-zinc-500 hover:text-black transition-colors">Início</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/noticias" class="text-sm text-zinc-500 hover:text-black transition-colors">Notícias do Setor</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/wiki" class="text-sm text-zinc-500 hover:text-black transition-colors">Wiki Inox</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/contato" class="text-sm text-zinc-500 hover:text-black transition-colors">Contato</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/rss.xml" class="text-sm text-zinc-500 hover:text-black transition-colors">RSS Feed</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Knowledge -->
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-zinc-900 mb-6">Conhecimento</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-4">
                    <li><a href="/wiki" class="text-sm text-zinc-500 hover:text-black transition-colors">Tipos de Aço</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/wiki" class="text-sm text-zinc-500 hover:text-black transition-colors">Aplicações Industriais</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/wiki" class="text-sm text-zinc-500 hover:text-black transition-colors">Tabelas Técnicas</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/wiki" class="text-sm text-zinc-500 hover:text-black transition-colors">Guia de Manutenção</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Newsletter Area -->
            <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-zinc-900 mb-6">Newsletter</h3>
                <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                    Assine para receber as últimas notícias do mercado e atualizações técnicas diretamente no seu e-mail.
                </p>
                <form class="space-y-2" aria-label="Assinar newsletter">
                    <div class="relative group">
                        <input 
                            type="email" 
                            placeholder="Seu melhor e-mail" 
                            aria-label="Seu e-mail para newsletter"
                            required
                            class="w-full bg-zinc-50 border border-zinc-100 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-black/5 focus:border-black transition-all outline-none"
                        />
                        <button type="submit" aria-label="Enviar inscrição" class="absolute right-2 top-2 bottom-2 bg-black text-white px-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-zinc-800 transition-colors">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m22 2-7 20-4-9-9-4Z"/><path d="M22 2 11 13"/></svg>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Bottom Bar -->
        <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-zinc-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-8 gap-y-4">
                <p class="text-[11px] font-medium text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest">
                    © {currentYear} Inox Link. Todos os direitos reservados.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-8">
                <a href="/privacidade" class="text-[11px] font-bold text-zinc-500 hover:text-black transition-colors uppercase tracking-widest">Privacidade</a>
                <a href="/termos" class="text-[11px] font-bold text-zinc-500 hover:text-black transition-colors uppercase tracking-widest">Termos</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>
